{
  "texts": [
    "We then compared the expression of 10 marker genes with the results of RNAscope generated on a parallel M1C tissue section (Methods).",
    "As shown in Fig. 2f and Supplementary Fig.",
    "4f, the spatial distribution of these marker genes in the same region demonstrates high concordance between RNAscope and DART-FISH.",
    "Specifically, the pan-excitatory neuron marker, SLC17A7, showed pronounced enrichment in the L2-L6 cortical layers.",
    "CUX2, RORB, and FEZF2 were enriched in supragranular, granular, and infragranular layers of the neocortex, respectively, which is consistent with previous studies [53] [54] [55] [56] [57]."
  ]
}